main event: A flashing orange and white beacon was sighted by a civilian at Tamiami Trail near U.S. 41.
interesting points: The sighting was reported on 18 November 1962,The object was observed for an unspecified duration,The direction and speed of the object were unknown,It was described as similar to an aircraft beacon but not standard in its flashing pattern,The object was later concluded to probably be an aircraft.
sighted object: one flashing orange and white beacon
